title: Fra Lippo Lippi - Light & Shade (1987)
description:
My favourite Norwegian band!

Great follow-up to the excellent Songs.  The bands last album for Virgin.  Released in 1987 and produced by Walter Becker.  Sounds very similar to the China's "Flaunt The Imperfection", which was again produced by WB.

1.  Angel
2.  Freedom
3.  Don't Take Away That Light
4.  Beauty & Madness
5.  Home
6.  Light & Shade
7.  Some People
8.  Crazy Wisdom
9.  Stardust Motel
10. Indifference

Ripped from original Virgin CD.
